Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Where the Sun Shines
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}WAVE\NWAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over here! You got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kishou Yanagihara. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama.\NCongrats on becoming the Newcomer King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KABUKI AGESEN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A commemoration match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Meijin Souya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just saying his name out loud{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}gave me goose bumps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In our country, he's the child of God.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it won't be at the Shogi Hall, as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Usually we do. But this year is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll invite people, get the press to cover it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and make it a huge event!\NLike boom, bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, on the same level as a title match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, um, why make such a...\NWhy so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking frankly, Kiriyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're aware of cases
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for the person who becomes the\NNewcomer King goes on to become a meijin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then, you're the fifth\Nmiddle school student in shogi history
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to become a professional right after Souya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's rooting for you\Nto become a meijin too, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A star showdown!\NThe current meijin versus the future meijin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}How can he say that so lightly?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But unlike our era,\Nyou've got Souya to contend with,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I feel sorry for you young guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He wasn't around in our day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Sure am glad I was born\Na long time ago. Kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he used to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back when Souya won his first title.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's already an old man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Souya's no old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he's the same age as Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a mystery\Nhow those two could be the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. What the hell happened\Nin Shimada's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SHINY SHINY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}DIM...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would swear that\NShimada's the same age as Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Shimada's still in his 30s, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can we change the subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are we going to do\Nabout this year's Kishou championship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My plan was to bill it as, "Sakurai 7th-Dan\Ntaking on his first title championship!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Association's Mountaineering Club
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Top Alpinist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.94,RightSignMC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Attack)>Invites people he likes\Nto the mountains\N(pretty tall ones)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had full media coverage ready,\Ndemonstration board commentary,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but then that moron Shimada...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody must be talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he already lost once,\Nhe just couldn't take the hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like an underdog, he clawed his way back up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then, in the third match to determine\Nthe challenger, he crushed it with an upset win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, would you give me a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Mr. Shimada has been\Nmaking an incredible effort too, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}(The voice of a Shimada fan)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagining what the posters might be like\Ngets me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}KISHOU CHAMPIONSHIP\NFIRST MATCH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MENTAL IMAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be any drabber?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The close-up profiles of two homely old men...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't even want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My heart won't even throb one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not young or flashy,\Nbut his playing is strong and tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have a single thing going for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling someone's saying\Nterrible things about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If people don't talk about this event,\Nwe'll lose sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Kishou Championship will be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, reality is harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}TURN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're doing us a solid here, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a solid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It means we're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You suddenly froze up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want some barley tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did I get home that night?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of things went in and out of my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It felt like I was floating,\Nso it was hard to walk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even after I got in bed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the lights reflected on the river kept glimmering\Nand swaying in front of my eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gently swaying...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the next day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}After School Shogi Science Club\NNow in Session!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Congratulations, Newcomer King Kiriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Congratulations, Newcomer King Kiriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay, now I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}have a toast to Kiriyama,\Nfor winning the title of Newcomer King.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'll explain the menu, a cornucopia\Nof the Shogi Science Club's scientific successes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}First, the soft drink we just made a toast with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}is homemade ginger ale!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We used fresh ginger\Nthat was growing behind the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next, Caspian Sea yogurt, we spared no effort\Nto grow it in the physics prep room's refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And freshly-gathered natto\Nwith rice flour dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Plum jam made from the plums\Noff the tree in front of the principal's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And finally, of course, our ramune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WAFT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you did great, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Yamazaki was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you really stuck it out, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you endured that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida was watching the live internet\Nbroadcast and he was so worked up over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was yelling and cheering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were about to kick us out of Mec's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I was excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a broadcast of my student's game,\Nwith a title on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "pretty"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that Pawn to 7-5 was a cool move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the edge of my seat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought we would get\Na Newcomer King from the Shogi Science Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about one of my comrades\Nis fighting a battle, I feel so proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not great at shogi,\Nbut I got so nervous just watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I need to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet their weird food\Nis giving you stomach pains!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Well, I mean...\N- Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what this is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}When did I get here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}To this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}warm place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone's waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It means we're counting on you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Congratulations. You worked really hard for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei, thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if what I suddenly gained...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will be lost just as suddenly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for now, I'm just happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so happy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}That's it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Even if it all does eventually disappear,\NI'll never forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll never forget there were days\Nwhen I was truly happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's Kiriyama. We meet again.\NEven though we already said goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's concentrating\Non choosing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}DIARY CORNER\N"Preserve Your Memories"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's leave him be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first page in the springtime of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think I'll get one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go with this ten-year one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I can take it out and remember anytime,\Nany number of times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where the Sun Shines
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Small World
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You should drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll warm you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, sit up a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get burned if it spills on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only I hadn't gotten sick,\Nwe'd be off the mountain by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a drag on you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I've become\Nsuch a nuisance to you, Gakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the mountains, we have to bear\Nthe burden of each other's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't think you were up for that,\NI would never have invited you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, I'm moved\Nby the tenacity you displayed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You put up a nice fight, Issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gakuto-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He taught me something that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He taught me that the most important thing\Nis to not give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think Gakuto-senpai will become\Nthe challenger for the Kishou Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PLAINLY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. He's totally brainwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from the fearful\NSakurai 7th-Dan's mountain therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Issa is innocent, so he was done in one hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Issa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He invites people he likes or his rivals\Nto the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,gets them in a jam,\Nand then treats them with kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,thereby gaining their trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the thing is, it's natural!\NHe has no evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.53,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gakuto Sakurai\NAge 30\NClass B-1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.53,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His refined behavior and kind smile\Nmake him the number one favorite\Nin the shogi world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary! Gakuto is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's got you surrounded by mountains,\Nhe takes over your mind completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}FLUFF\NFLUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he probably can't beat\NSakurai in a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gakuto-senpai, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Gakuto has invited\NMr. Shimada before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mountains, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had my fill of the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}STAB
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}HAHAHA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}MIDDLE SCHOOL STUDENT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was a little kid,\NI got dropped off in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}PACK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and told not to come back home until I filled up\Nmy pack with bamboo shoots and vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}ROCK CLIMBING\NIN SWEAT PANTS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can I put it?\NThat was part of my daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I think I've had enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's Shimada 8th-Dan for you,\Na natural-born mountain climber!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So cool! A man with a heart\Nthat not even a therapist can access!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's starting to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Loose Stone Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I took that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he would take my pawn at 4-2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I went with the same, upper gold general,\Nhe would capture my 9-7 bishop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even promoting my rook and going to 8-9,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he would move his Bishop to 4-2\Nand get promoted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}DRAGON HORSE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I'd be crushed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, I'll just move\Nmy bishop to 8-9, promoted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}RUMBLE\NRUMBLE\NCRASH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Falling Rocks Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Shimada 8th-Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He handles even an avalanche of powerful pieces\Nwith his usual aplomb! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gakuto will be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it would be better if Sakurai 7th-Dan wins,\Nso we can get more readers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? It looks like Shimada is going to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saku, keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, no one will come\Nto the Kishou Championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada, let's take a hint here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over! We don't know yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gakuto-senpai never gives up and right now,\Nhis determination will cover the board...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He uses his pawn at 5-1,\Nthen after the same, Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he captures the 4-8 pawn\Nand gold general.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's in trouble with the same,\Nupper gold general and lance at 4-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The pawn is about to be promoted,\Nso he's got no defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada is the challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Toku, let's go drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Kishou Championship,\Nmy tenth win is on the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and my opponent is Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurai has a bright personality,\Nand he's still green.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He would've been the perfect opponent for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, things don't always go\Nthe way you want them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure if you leave Shimada alone,\Nhe'll just start winning again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotou was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have charm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but he's bulked up some more,\Nand came back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My tenth go-round\Nwith the Kishou Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've better literally defend it to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I won the challenger's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It brings me shivers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And not metaphorically...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... My stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}After School Shogi Science Club\NNow in Session!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could I have forgotten?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Retiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}TWIRL TWIRL\NTWIST TWIST
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Trying to make straw sandals\Nwith the straw gathered\Nfrom last year's rice crop\N(for summer sandals)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Kiriyama, other than you,\Nwe're all third-years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}3RD-YEARS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so after summer vacation is over,\Nwe have to focus on university entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're all third-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, just like that, I lost the one place\Nin school where I belonged.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kiriyama going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's gotten a little more\Ncheerful lately, but now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Gaining" and "losing" things\Nare an unavoidable part of life for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You feel joy, you feel disappointment,\Nand it repeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how you learn\Nhow to handle your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Disappointment and loneliness\Nare necessary emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Because of loneliness,\Npeople muster courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}and reach out to a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:20:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doing that is like reaching out as a baby does,\Nand expands its small world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GRAB
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even alone, I can go over game records,\Nexamine past data,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come up with strategies for my next match,\Nsolve tsume-shogi problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Fully intending\Non holing up inside school\N(Too much sadness\Nmade him throw away logic.)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}HEAPS...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, somebody get me paper and a marker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I said I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, there's a ton of stuff\NI can do by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like researching new players\Nor coming up with countermeasures...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what a club is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SHOGI CLUB\NCOME JOIN!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put up the new member\Nrecruitment poster! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}STUDENT COUNCIL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Shogi Science Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know we even had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking for members now?\NThat's probably a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Went to Student Council\Nto get stamp of approval
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have my blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Komahashi High School\NStudent Council Seal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Thanks.\N- Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, the issue was soon resolved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama! Some people\Nwho want to join the club are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They saw your poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good gracious, isn't this amazing, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you're the principal and vice-principal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you transferred here,\NI wanted to have you teach me shogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I kept sending Hayashida\Nrequests to join the Shogi Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it was exasperating because he would\Nalways say, "Right now is a little..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Kiriyama didn't want\Nhis professional status to be public.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the head teacher, Nakamura,\Nsaid he wants to join too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Including Mr. Hayashida,\Nyou've got five members.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can continue on as the Shogi Club alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they're all bigwigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:22:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, um, clubs are supposed to have\Nat least five student members...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's trivial! Kiriyama,\Ndo you know who this man is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's the principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So getting around these things is easy peasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would like to put my own stamp on\Nthe academy in a positive way, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd like our Hashi High team to make B class\Nin the Career Group Shogi Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely within our range.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now we have acquired\Nthe ultimate coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hasn't this now become\Nmore of a shogi class than a shogi club?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, with the admission of a few unexpected\Nnew members, the club can now continue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new adventure begins for Rei Kiriyama\Nand the jolly members.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Science Club\NNow in Session!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One summer afternoon,\Nwith the science division gone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Club\N*Currently Looking for Student Members
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Shogi Science Club\Nsimply became the Shogi Club{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the average member age\Nincreased to 24 years old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Small World
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.60,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 34
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone. It's gone. It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.31,0:24:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this\Nkeep happening lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.27,0:24:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brown-noser...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.64,0:24:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I would hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, do you believe that I hid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be it a parent-teacher conference,\Nor whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.73,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be on your side, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:59.04,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ILLUSTRATION:\NHYOGONOSUKE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.90,0:24:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Issa, the mountains aren't going\Nto get any bigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.95,0:24:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we have\Na lot of room to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.08,0:24:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Gakuto-senpai!
